Một vòng nữa.

361
00:51:59,090 --> 00:52:01,380
Sigurd!

362
00:52:01,550 --> 00:52:03,500
Đạn!

363
00:52:07,170 --> 00:52:08,460
Evensen?

364
00:52:09,960 --> 00:52:12,050
